title: MAGIC JEWELS
description: Help the little genie in her magic shop and serve the fairies beautiful jewels! Swap and match at least 3 gems in a row to remove them from the field. Combining 4 or more stones will create special gems which explode full lines, destroy all gems of a single color or clear certain areas. Fulfill all orders to complete a level and use powerful boosters when you're stuck. Earn extra coins by completing goals, battle against mighty bosses and try to beat all 101 levels!
